    "slides": [
        {
            "id": "s_l1_1",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Document Object Model 🌳",
            "content": "When a web page loads, the browser creates a **DOM** of the page.\n\nIt treats every HTML tag (`<div>`, `<h1>`, `<p>`) as an **Object** in a tree structure."
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l1_2",
